<div id="contacts-tab" title="Contacts">

  <h3>Important Telephone numbers</h3>



  <p><strong>Emergency Hotlines</strong><br />

  Police – 999<br />

  Ambulance – 995<br />

  Fire Brigade – 995<br />

  Flight Information – 1800 542 4422</p>



  <p><strong>Medical Services</strong><br />

  Raffles Hospital (585 North Bridge Road) – (65) 6311 1111<br />

  Singapore General Hospital (Outram Road) – (65) 6222 3322<br />

  Gleneagles Hospital (6A Napier Road) – (65) 6473 7222</p>



  <p><strong>Credit Cards</strong><br />

  American Express – 1800 396 6000<br />

  JCB – (65) 6734 0096<br />

  Diners Card – (65) 6416 0800<br />

  Visa – 800 448 1250<br />

  MasterCard – 800 110 0113</p>



  <p><strong>Foreign Embassies</strong><br />

  Germany (50 Raffles Place) – (65) 6533 6002<br />

  Australia (25 Napier Road) – (65) 6836 4100<br />

  USA (27 Napier Road) – (65) 6476 9100<br />

  UK (100 Tanglin Road) – 6424 4200<br />

  Canada (1 George Street) – (65) 6854 5900<br />

  France (101 Cluny Park Road) – (65) 6880 7800</p>



  <p>For more embassies, <a href="http://www.embassiesabroad.com/embassies-in/Singapore/index.html">click here.</a></p>

